{"id": "art-297", "label": "Art. 297", "title": "Art. 297: Lipsa încuviinţărilor cerute de lege", "slug": "art-297", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 297: Lipsa încuviin&#355;&#259;rilor cerute de lege </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Este anulabil&#259;\nc&#259;s&#259;toria încheiat&#259; f&#259;r&#259; încuviin&#355;&#259;rile sau\nautorizarea prev&#259;zute la art. 272 alin. (2), (4) &#351;i (5).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1920240532\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1166\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1920240532\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Anulabilitatea poate fi invocat&#259; numai de cel a\nc&#259;rui încuviin&#355;are era necesar&#259;. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 46 alin.\n(3) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}